---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---
<BaseLayout title="Request a Gardening or Landscaping Job | Wooden Bone Garden and Landscape Adelaide" description="Send photos. Get a practical next step.">
<section class="section topo"><div class="container"><h1>Send photos. Get a practical next step.</h1><p>Tell John what needs sorting, upload photos, and get practical guidance.</p><p><span class="badge">Practical, Reliable & Local</span><span class="badge">Direct With John</span></p>
<div class="form-wrap"><div class="prog"><i id="bar" style="width:20%"></i></div>
<form name="request-job" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" action="/thank-you" enctype="multipart/form-data" data-track-submit><input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="request-job"/><p hidden><label>Don’t fill this out: <input name="bot-field"/></label></p>
<div class="step active"><h2>Step 1 · What needs doing?</h2>{['Garden cleanup','Regular maintenance','Lawn and edges','Weeding','Irrigation','Turf','Planting','Small landscaping','Pre-sale tidy-up','Not sure'].map(i=><label class="choice"><input type="checkbox" name="needs" value={i}/> {i}</label>)}<button class="btn btn-primary next" type="button">Next</button></div>
<div class="step"><h2>Step 2 · How big is the job?</h2><label class="choice"><input type="radio" name="size" value="Small tidy-up" required/> Small tidy-up</label><label class="choice"><input type="radio" name="size" value="Half-day"/> Half-day</label><label class="choice"><input type="radio" name="size" value="Full-day"/> Full-day</label><label class="choice"><input type="radio" name="size" value="Multi-day"/> Multi-day</label><label class="choice"><input type="radio" name="size" value="Not sure"/> Not sure</label><button class="btn btn-ghost prev" type="button">Back</button> <button class="btn btn-primary next" type="button">Next</button></div>
<div class="step"><h2>Step 3 · Where are you?</h2><label>Suburb<input required name="suburb"/></label><label>Address (optional)<input name="address"/></label><button class="btn btn-ghost prev" type="button">Back</button> <button class="btn btn-primary next" type="button">Next</button></div>
<div class="step"><h2>Step 4 · Show the garden</h2><p>Photos help John understand the job before visiting.</p><label class="upload-drop">Drag and drop photos here, or tap to upload.<input type="file" name="photos" multiple onchange="window.wbgTrack&&window.wbgTrack('photo_upload')"/></label><label>Describe the job<textarea name="description"></textarea></label><button class="btn btn-ghost prev" type="button">Back</button> <button class="btn btn-primary next" type="button">Next</button></div>
<div class="step"><h2>Step 5 · Contact details</h2><label>Name<input required name="name"/></label><label>Mobile<input required name="mobile"/></label><label>Email<input type="email" required name="email"/></label><label>Preferred contact<select name="preferred_contact"><option>Phone</option><option>SMS</option><option>Email</option></select></label><label><input type="checkbox" required name="consent"/> Your details are only used to respond to your job request.</label><button class="btn btn-ghost prev" type="button">Back</button> <button class="btn btn-rust" type="submit">Send Job Request</button></div>
</form></div><p>For urgent jobs, calling or texting may be faster: <a data-track="phone_click" href={`tel:${site.phone}`}>Call</a> · <a data-track="sms_click" href={`sms:${site.sms}`}>SMS</a></p></div></section>
<script is:inline>
const s=[...document.querySelectorAll('.step')];let i=0;window.wbgTrack&&window.wbgTrack('form_start');const u=()=>{s.forEach((e,n)=>e.classList.toggle('active',n===i));document.getElementById('bar').style.width=`${(i+1)/s.length*100}%`;};document.querySelectorAll('.next').forEach(b=>b.onclick=()=>{window.wbgTrack&&window.wbgTrack('form_step_complete',{step:i+1});i=Math.min(i+1,s.length-1);u();});document.querySelectorAll('.prev').forEach(b=>b.onclick=()=>{i=Math.max(0,i-1);u();});
</script>
</BaseLayout>
